ğŸ§ª Example: Mistaken instance_type change

Old:

Always show details

instance_type = "t2.micro"

New:

Always show details

instance_type = "t3.large"

ğŸ” Rollback Steps:

Always show details

git revert OR git checkout <old-commit>
terraform plan
terraform apply

